line_1: This Boy he kept each Band to disengage,
line_2: He was, to weet, a little roguish Page,

line_1: This Boy he kept each Band to disengage,
line_2: Like most the untaught Striplings of his Age.

line_1: This Boy he kept each Band to disengage,

line_2: Could war with sacred folly wage;
From the dread bonds of many an age,
